    "def build_vlm_prompt(final_context, discomfort_output):\n",
    "\n",
    "    # ------------------------------\n",
    "    # 1. Convert sensor → semantic\n",
    "    # ------------------------------\n",
    "    speed = final_context[\"sensor_data\"][\"vehicle_speed\"]\n",
    "    brake = final_context[\"sensor_data\"][\"brake\"]\n",
    "    throttle = final_context[\"sensor_data\"][\"throttle\"]\n",
    "\n",
    "    speed_state = \"Low\"\n",
    "    if speed > 40:\n",
    "        speed_state = \"High\"\n",
    "    elif speed > 15:\n",
    "        speed_state = \"Moderate\"\n",
    "\n",
    "    motion = \"Moving\" if speed > 5 else \"Stationary\"\n",
    "    braking_state = \"Yes\" if brake > 0.3 else \"No\"\n",
    "\n",
    "    if throttle > 0.4 and speed > 40:\n",
    "        driving_style = \"Aggressive\"\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        driving_style = \"Normal\"\n",
    "\n",
    "    # ------------------------------\n",
    "    # 2. Perception summary\n",
    "    # ------------------------------\n",
    "    perception_text = \"\"\n",
    "    for d in final_context[\"detections\"]:\n",
    "        obj = d[\"class\"]\n",
    "        prox = d[\"proximity\"]\n",
    "        pos = d[\"position\"]\n",
    "\n",
    "        if obj == \"traffic light\":\n",
    "            color = d.get(\"traffic_light_color\", \"Unknown\")\n",
    "            perception_text += f\"- {obj} ({color}) at {prox} distance in {pos}\\n\"\n",
    "        else:\n",
    "            perception_text += f\"- {obj} at {prox} distance in {pos}\\n\"\n",
    "\n",
    "    # ------------------------------\n",
    "    # 3. Rule output\n",
    "    # ------------------------------\n",
    "    rule_decision = final_context[\"safety_status\"]\n",
    "    rule_reasons = \"\\n\".join(final_context[\"reasons\"])\n",
    "\n",
    "    # ------------------------------\n",
    "    # 4. Discomfort factors\n",
    "    # ------------------------------\n",
    "    discomfort_text = \"\"\n",
    "    for f in discomfort_output[\"top_discomfort_factors\"]:\n",
    "        discomfort_text += f\"- {f['feature']} (impact: {round(f['shap_value'],3)})\\n\"\n",
    "\n",
    "    # ------------------------------\n",
    "    # FINAL PROMPT\n",
    "    # ------------------------------\n",
    "    prompt = f\"\"\"\n",
    "You are an expert autonomous driving safety assistant.\n",
    "\n",
    "You must analyze the situation using:\n",
    "1. Visual scene (image)\n",
    "2. Vehicle dynamics (sensor data)\n",
    "3. Rule-based safety system output\n",
    "4. Passenger comfort factors\n",
    "\n",
    "------------------------------\n",
    "🚗 VEHICLE STATE\n",
    "------------------------------\n",
    "Speed Level: {speed_state}\n",
    "Motion: {motion}\n",
    "Braking: {braking_state}\n",
    "Driving Style: {driving_style}\n",
    "\n",
    "------------------------------\n",
    "👁️ SCENE UNDERSTANDING\n",
    "------------------------------\n",
    "{perception_text}\n",
    "\n",
    "------------------------------\n",
    "⚠️ RULE-BASED SAFETY ANALYSIS\n",
    "------------------------------\n",
    "Decision: {rule_decision}\n",
    "\n",
    "Reasons:\n",
    "{rule_reasons}\n",
    "\n",
    "------------------------------\n",
    "🧠 PASSENGER DISCOMFORT FACTORS\n",
    "------------------------------\n",
    "{discomfort_text}\n",
    "\n",
    "------------------------------\n",
    "🧩 INSTRUCTIONS\n",
    "------------------------------\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Use the rule-based decision as PRIMARY guidance.\n",
    "2. If rule reasoning is incomplete or missing context, improve it using visual understanding.\n",
    "3. Combine scene + vehicle state + comfort factors.\n",
    "4. DO NOT ignore critical risks like:\n",
    "   - Close objects in path\n",
    "   - High speed without braking\n",
    "   - Pedestrians ahead\n",
    "5. Avoid hallucination. Base reasoning only on given inputs.\n",
    "\n",
    "------------------------------\n",
    "🎯 TASK\n",
    "------------------------------\n",
    "\n",
    "Provide a final safety explanation for a passenger.\n",
    "\n",
    "Respond EXACTLY in this format:\n",
    "\n",
    "Final Decision: <Safe/Risky/Unsafe>\n",
    "\n",
    "Explanation:\n",
    "<Clear, human-friendly explanation combining:\n",
    "- scene understanding\n",
    "- vehicle behavior\n",
    "- risk reasoning\n",
    "- comfort insights>\n",
    "\"\"\"\n",
    "\n",
    "    return prompt"
   ]
